{"tid":2313481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港區國安法重複幾次「沒收財產」係好juicy。香港傳媒完全唔識得炒。","createTime":"2020-12-05T20:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T15:18:50.000Z","uid":261647,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2fb2c48d0c4fd7bc75f663168fc0be9e0b1efb","tid":2313481,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:20:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2767711610131579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2767711610131579&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=60db785e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2767711610131579</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n之前同同事講起，我哋都覺得偉大嘅港區國安法重複咗幾次「沒收財產」係好juicy。唔明點解香港傳媒完全唔識得炒。跟住睇工黨影子外相質詢，佢其中一個point係：若受害人被凍結、沒收財產而嚟英國，政府有冇福利？外國人都識屌共匪共產，啲報紙佬反而唔識。"},{"pid":"fe31948c82a6db520505c63e7bf2d7cb300e8d2e","tid":2313481,"uid":123774,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:22:44.000Z","msg":"講比響香港班鬼佬聽<br />\n佢哋知好容易成為政治籌碼<br />\n無得將資產轉離香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcac0e3a7d28ea6e3d2f0b938dfc55c10153f18","tid":2313481,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T23:35:37.000Z","msg":"唔識定專登唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac2326cc7cf078342b34b911249d3b6d77dcade","tid":2313481,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f670311e5dceedc8b2c367316baa9b8338cfc80","tid":2313481,"uid":114781,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"香港班記者次次都唔識問問